{"tid":548250,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個遇過最顛嘅老細","createTime":"2018-02-02T10:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T01:40:14.000Z","uid":166822,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"721201318d6c57a4ccf89b79f962e9745da3ec66","tid":548250,"uid":166822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"[member] 我老細顛到會計住我去咗幾耐廁所 又問我點解會去咁耐 就黎人都顛 [member]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9b25cd93c213e876e2e98579676b6d313596c4","tid":548250,"uid":166675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"叫佢跟埋入來係佢面前痾囉"},{"pid":"b06d89d668bdd8f66196963b7560fb20ad570634","tid":548250,"uid":133824,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩出黎做學師果時有次個老闆一齊去個客到check冷氣<br />\n係38樓爬出窗口因為無企位扒左係部散熱機頂攬到實一實度磅，入番黎個客見我咁搏臨走俾左一舊水貼士<br />\n出到門口我老闆問我拎果一舊水黎，我以為一人一半都俾番50蚊我啦，點知佢拎完就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da897b5a80b2d90b99c5918543be171ad1c29812","tid":548250,"uid":77723,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b06d89d668bdd8f66196963b7560fb20ad570634","tid":548250,"uid":133824,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"岩岩出黎做學師果時有次個老闆一齊去個客到check冷氣<br />\n係38樓爬出窗口因為無企位扒左係部散熱機頂攬到實一實度磅，入番黎個客見我咁搏臨走俾左一舊水貼士<br />\n出到門口我老闆問我拎果一舊水黎，我以為一人一半都俾番50蚊我啦，點知佢拎完就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"正一卜街"},{"pid":"db2af8bc2f632c2ca3e660fbd0d6dbd971429aba","tid":548250,"uid":150294,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T11:07:33.000Z","msg":"猶太佬，發脾氣一腳踢穿左幅牆！"},{"pid":"a5419ceaf8d4a8f1e94b9e4f0bc5881e21c5280f","tid":548250,"uid":64131,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"cited